				\begin{document}$$ \mathrm{R}\left(\mathrm{year}\right)=1\hbox{-} {\left(1\hbox{-} \mathrm{R}\left(\mathrm{contact}\right)\right)}^{\times } $$\end{document}Ryear=1‐1‐Rcontact×

